g.text: 1. As a user, I would like to be able to see a list of articles.
2. As a user, I would like to be able to see a list of topics.
3. As a user, I would like to be able to see a list of articles by topic.
4. As a user, I would like to be able to see a list of users.
5. As a user, I would like to be able to see a list of articles by user.
6. As a user, I would like to be able to see one article in focus,
7. As a user, I would like to be able to comment on an article.
8. As a user, I would like to vote on an article.
9. Any Create, Update or Delete operations should only be available to
10. As a user, I would like to be able to make myself active on the app.
